同steakland都食過，就算steakland lunch 叫到最貴果餐，你都唔會食到期待果隻神戶牛感覺，我唔想佢浪費左果7千yen姐<br />\n<br />\n我唔係有錢人，但既然佢有期待，覺得佢應該加多d budget，唔會令佢失望</blockquote><br />\nmouriya係咪ok?佢個價我同男友都覺得ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsteakland一定唔考慮，太遊客生意，多數都唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOk呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢網好似有coupon同記得訂位"},{"pid":"a23f7abe54d419be8a9e8dd6a6cd64d39e19c162","tid":92440,"uid":76866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:18:16.000Z","msg":"可以試下 Garaku, 兩次去神户都係去依度 lunch.... <br />\nLunch menu 由 4000 到10000 yen 都有"},{"pid":"af41e95751442fc42d58a91d366b4b76ff6e9874","tid":92440,"uid":19062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:04:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>mourinya</blockquote><br />\n7000yen budget喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食過 午市好人差唔多價 有得book 位"},{"pid":"c4f0142c79e15833b3352041c582848a3860cf5c","tid":92440,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:17:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去日本竟然食神戶牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個用來出口坤外國人既低級野但又貴到hihi<br />\n<br />\n日本各地都有優良本地牛<br />\n使鬼食貴價</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正確黎講不論神戶牛或松阪牛都唔係一個品種而係一個品牌，兩者既品種都係來自兵庫縣既但馬牛，只係從幼年但馬年當中挑選較優質既牛隻賣去神戶松阪或日本各地由當地地區特定方法去飼養，所以如果話神戶牛用黎坤外國人我就不敢苟同。"},{"pid":"b877c0cd85ecd0156d17ff7921d86c140f2d6f9c","tid":92440,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:35:24.000Z","msg":"上次晚餐試過京都白川既 itoh-dining，神戶都有一間，lunch 大概 8000 yen ，可以一戰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i238.photobucket.com/albums/ff47/ashleyroad/KYOTO%202015/DSCF0250.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi238.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fff47%2Fashleyroad%2FKYOTO%25202015%2FDSCF0250.jpg&h=49b449fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i238.photobucket.com/albums/ff47/ashleyroad/KYOTO%202015/DSCF0315-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi238.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fff47%2Fashleyroad%2FKYOTO%25202015%2FDSCF0315-2.jpg&h=7d61554b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2b2fadc2cf4198cfa2710fede413e46cfc9b232","tid":92440,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T03:19:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去日本竟然食神戶牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個用來出口坤外國人既低級野但又貴到hihi<br />\n<br />\n日本各地都有優良本地牛<br />\n使鬼食貴價</blockquote><br />\n你知唔知但馬牛而家都係限制出口，去到神戶先有最頂級同正宗食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔識就唔好衝出嚟柒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7fa90b04500cefe9cfa562336faac38aeb6e2d","tid":92440,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:23:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>神戶牛好油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n油唔油係睇你食JMGA咩grade，你食A5就算咩品種都會油，同神唔神戶冇關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999f2072cb5084da6da754ee5e86dfb9a6cd1d5c","tid":92440,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:35:22.000Z","msg":"留名睇介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e130b424c9cebb280ec97a699e0383ed74395dcb","tid":92440,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:50:40.000Z","msg":"7000 羊可能唔夠<br />\n<br />\n上次入左間名店，差唔多九千先食到神牛<br />\n<br />\n有平啲，但係好似係但到牛黎"},{"pid":"99afc67aa8fbb6a610718a1a092dd765b94293fd","tid":92440,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:51:09.000Z","msg":"7000 羊可能唔夠<br />\n<br />\n上次入左間名店，差唔多九千先食到神牛<br />\n<br />\n有平啲，但係好似係但丁牛黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw 最後訂位，可能無位"},{"pid":"b1a2388844d56c7b224e08edf293d305845629fe","tid":92440,"uid":34468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"